        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Jaucribaix in Norg (K-8) to begin the quest.\n2. Speak to Aeka (I-8) to receive Oriental Steel.\n3. Speak to Ranemaud (I-7) to receive a Sacred Sprig.\n4. Travel to Konschtat Highlands (D-8), trade the Oriental Steel to the ??? inside the cave to spawn a Bomb Notorious Monster named Forger, approximately level 33.\n   - The level 99 Unity warp (Sleepy Mabel) will place you close to this point at (G-7).\n5. Once the Forger is defeated, a Bomb Steel will drop.\n   - If you are defeated while fighting the Forger or somehow lose the Bomb Steel before the next part, Aeka can give you another Oriental Steel in exchange for a Darksteel Ore.\n   - If you are doing the quest for multiple people, you must wait 4 minutes to re-spawn the Forger for another Bomb Steel.\n6. Purchase a Hatchet and travel to The Sanctuary of Zi\'Tah. You will find an area off of the map in the northern part of (K-10) that will take you to a block at (L-9).  There you will find a ??? spot you may reach by climbing up a nearby rock.  Use the Hatchet on the ??? spot to spawn a Treant Notorious Monster named Guardian Treant.\n   - The level 122 Unity warp (Keeper of Heiligtum) will place you close to this point at (K-12).\n   - If you are doing the quest for multiple people, you only need to kill the Treant once.\n7. Once the Treant is defeated, trade the Sacred Sprig to the ??? to receive a Sacred Branch.\n8. Trade the Bomb Steel and the Sacred Branch to Jaucribaix.\n9. Return in 72 in-game hours (3 real-life hours) to receive your reward.',
