        walkthrough = '1. To begin this quest in your log, you need the Serpent Rumors key item.  It can be purchased from Fennella in Port Windurst (C-8) for 95,000 Guild Points with Fishing rank Adept or higher.\n   - You can still obtain the other items needed for this quest before initiating it.\n2. Turn in Liks and Gugrusaurus to Zaldon to obtain Opal Silk and Saber Shoot, respectively.\n   - About a ~.5% chance to get each.\n3. Speak to Irmilant in Rabao (G-7).\n4. Trade the Opal Silk and Saber Shoot to Irmilant.\n5. Return to Irmilant after conquest tally to receive your reward.',
