        previous = nil,
        next = nil,
        requirements = nil,
        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Rauteinot who asks for a slab of Elshimo Marble.\n   - Elshimo Marble drops off Ivory Lizard in Yuhtunga Jungle.\n2. Trade the Elshimo Marble to Rauteinot. You will receive Rauteinot\'s parcel.\n3. Head to Northern San d\'Oria and speak to Mulaujeant at (E-5) near the Blacksmithing guild on the second floor.\n4. Wait until one Earth minute has passed and speak to Mulaujeant again to be given the Sublime statue of the Goddess.\n5. Return to Rauteinot for your reward.',
